                        <p>This is a letter from Fr John  J. Murphy C.S.Sp., a Congregation of the Holy Spirit priest in Kimmage, Dublin, to Rev Dr John F. Hogan (1858-1918). Hogan was a priest, author, and president of St Patrick&#39;s College, Maynooth.</p>
                    
                        <p>In the letter, Fr Hogan agrees to conduct a retreat to mark the start of the scholastic year and requests instructions to carry it out.</p>
                    
